<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 14:21:05 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以太币和隐私币导致损失，加密货币暴跌加剧</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-05/ether-and-privacy-coins-lead-latest-losses-as-crypto-plummets</link><description>由于数字资产在经历了艰难的一周后继续遭受严重损失，以太币跌至一年多来的最低水平。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iJcA.uTjm7M8/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 07:29:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-05/ether-and-privacy-coins-lead-latest-losses-as-crypto-plummets</guid></item><item><title>币安关系推动特朗普家族的稳定币财富</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-05/trump-family-s-stablecoin-wealth-fueled-by-binance-relationship</link><description>特朗普家族的一家加密货币企业通过进军稳定币获得了丰厚的利润，部分归功于与币安控股有限公司的促销安排。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iVKkNc9k1_tQ/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 12:00:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-05/trump-family-s-stablecoin-wealth-fueled-by-binance-relationship</guid></item><item><title>加密货币溃败加剧，比特币国债损失 620 亿美元</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-05/bitcoin-treasury-firms-shed-62-billion-in-deepening-crypto-rout</link><description>比特币本周的下跌给近期加密货币热潮中出现的最雄心勃勃的金融实验之一增添了新的压力：为代表投资者积累数字资产而创建的上市公司。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iurMaImOFPzY/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 04:00:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-05/bitcoin-treasury-firms-shed-62-billion-in-deepening-crypto-rout</guid></item><item><title>美国众议院主要委员会正在准备立法以制定加密货币税收结构</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-04/key-us-house-committee-preparing-legislation-to-forge-crypto-tax-structure</link><description>负责税收政策的众议院小组正在准备立法，以解决加密货币的税收问题，最早将于周五发布，下周初将举行听证会。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iQWwstahc5G8/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2026 23:58:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-04/key-us-house-committee-preparing-legislation-to-forge-crypto-tax-structure</guid></item><item><title>不再需要比特币的区块链正在获得动力</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-04/blockchain-no-longer-needing-bitcoin-is-gaining-momentum</link><description>金融科技对产品比代币价格更感兴趣。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/isIkrVfDkPpc/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-06-04/blockchain-no-longer-needing-bitcoin-is-gaining-momentum</guid></item><item><title>塞勒的比特币机器每个气缸都失火了</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-04/michael-saylor-s-bitcoin-machine-is-misfiring-on-every-cylinder</link><description>Michael Saylor 围绕一个简单的想法创建了 Strategy Inc.：筹集资金购买比特币，然后永远不要出售它。随着时间的推移，这个简单的赌注变得更加复杂。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i2Qy.ZajUlDw/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 04 Jun 2026 16:10:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-04/michael-saylor-s-bitcoin-machine-is-misfiring-on-every-cylinder</guid></item><item><title>战略抛售引发溃败后，比特币与科技股的差距扩大</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-03/bitcoin-s-break-with-tech-widens-as-strategy-s-sale-feeds-rout</link><description>在Strategy Inc.出售其庞大加密货币库存的一小部分之后，比特币的抛售一直持续到周三，这扰乱了市场情绪，并扩大了该代币与创纪录的科技股之间的差距。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iaTE4QmyBCK4/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2026 06:25:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-03/bitcoin-s-break-with-tech-widens-as-strategy-s-sale-feeds-rout</guid></item><item><title>随着比特币的融化，180％的加密货币反弹显示了新的投资时代</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-03/a-180-crypto-rally-shows-new-investing-era-as-bitcoin-stumbles</link><description>随着数十亿美元离开比特币和以太基金，资金正在流入加密货币的一个角落，这承诺了投资者长期以来在数字资产中难以找到的东西：从经济活动到代币价值的更清晰的路径。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iTOFRhQJR_aA/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 03 Jun 2026 13:46:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-03/a-180-crypto-rally-shows-new-investing-era-as-bitcoin-stumbles</guid></item></channel></rss>